{"tid":1120439,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中年漢港鐵大圍站墮軌亡　東鐵線全線服務受阻","createTime":"2019-04-22T16:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T14:30:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1d314aed0a7eb5471794aa50373807f940df29e5","tid":1120439,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T16:02:11.000Z","msg":"一名40歲男子晚上約10時半，於港鐵大圍鐵路站2號月台墮軌，其間有列車駛至，他被捲入車底。消防和救援人員到場拯救，證實男子當場死亡。港鐵表示，閉路電視錄影片段顯示，有乘客自行跳入路軌。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵宣布九龍塘站往返沙田站服務暫停，紅磡站往返九龍塘站，及沙田站往返羅湖站，列車每10分鐘一班。港鐵正安排免費接駁巴士到場，同時呼籲乘客考慮使用其他交通工具。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線：2382 0000<br />\n<br />\n撒瑪利亞防止自殺會：2389 2222<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署：2343 2255<br />\n<br />\n明愛向晴軒：18288<br />\n<br />\n年輕人專線<br />\n<br />\n香港輔導及心理學會：WhatsApp熱線6218 1084 (提供英語及粵語專業輔導服務)<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線：青少年生命專線 2382 0777<br />\n<br />\n賽馬會青少年網上輔導平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"https://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0hOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=cb6a988d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190422/s00001/1555944256955/中年漢港鐵大圍站墮軌亡-東鐵線全線服務受阻\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190422%2Fs00001%2F1555944256955%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E7%AB%99%E5%A2%AE%E8%BB%8C%E4%BA%A1-%E6%9D%B1%E9%90%B5%E7%B7%9A%E5%85%A8%E7%B7%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E5%8F%97%E9%98%BB&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0hOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=16ae63b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190422%2Fs00001%2F1555944256955%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E7%AB%99%E5%A2%AE%E8%BB%8C%E4%BA%A1-%E6%9D%B1%E9%90%B5%E7%B7%9A%E5%85%A8%E7%B7%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E5%8F%97%E9%98%BB&h=57c0b1a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/201